I"b<ol>
  <li>Install Module:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>apt-get <span class="nb">install </span>xtables-addons-dkms
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Tarpit Source IP:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>iptables <span class="nt">-A</span> INPUT <span class="nt">-p</span> tcp <span class="nt">-s</span> &lt;<span class="nv">$SOURCE_IP</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="nt">-j</span> TARPIT
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

<hr />

<p>Remove Source IP from Tarpit:</p>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>iptables <span class="nt">-D</span> INPUT <span class="nt">-p</span> tcp <span class="nt">-s</span> &lt;<span class="nv">$SOURCE_IP</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="nt">-j</span> TARPIT
</code></pre></div></div>

